  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
      <div rend="parallel">
        <lg xml:id="Aink408">
          <l>pāṇar mullai pāṭac cuṭariḻai</l>
          <l>vāṇuta larivai mullai malaiya</l>
          <l>viṉitirun taṉaṉē neṭuntakai</l>
          <l>tuṉitīr koḷkaittaṉ putalvaṉoṭu polintē</l>
        </lg>
        <p xml:lang="en">
          As the bard sang the mullai [scale], and the young woman with the shining jewels and bright forehead wore jasmine flowers, [there] the paragon sat sweetly beaming, with his son whose conduct is free from disgust.
        </p>
      </div>
